    "body": "Applies the appropriate `DiagnosticSign*` highlight to each group, resetting the highlights at the end of the expression.\r\n\r\n<img width=\"532\" height=\"86\" alt=\"image\" src=\"https://github.com/user-attachments/assets/bbd147ad-398a-4c90-80a6-0ec62a0dee09\" />\r\n\r\n---\r\n\r\nRelated to #35152\r\n\r\nIt might be worth having a `pretty` argument which determines whether or not to add these highlights, but at this point it might be better just to have a format function as discussed in the above issue\r\n",
