            "author_association": "MEMBER",
            "body": "> * Ability to not use highlight groups. I'd expect that to be a default behavior.\r\n> * Ability to adjust highlight groups **or** introduce dedicated `DiagnosticStatuslineXxx` groups.\r\n\r\nThis is covered by https://github.com/neovim/neovim/issues/35152 . \r\n\r\nThe purpose of status() is to do something reasonable with minimal config. Any customizations are covered by the escape hatch, whatever it turns out to be.\r\n\r\nFor now we can just force a bg color. Or use a slightly darker default StatusLine.",
